com.esri.mo2.cs.geod
Interface Projection

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, CoordinateSystem, Equivalency, GeodeticObject, NamedObject, PEObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseProjection
public interface Projection
extends GeodeticObject, PEObject, NamedObject, CoordinateSystem

represents a geodetic projection that transforms coordinates to and from geographic coordinates. All conversions assume coordinates are in radians or meters: the xyz coordinates are assumed metric (so they need to be converted if they are not) the latitude longitude coordinates are assumed to be radians; longitude corresponds to x; latitude corresponds to y;
